Driver Safety Tip #9: CLEAN YOUR WINDSHIELD [especially for night driving]. During the day, a dirty windshield, while annoying, is pretty harmless. However, at nighttime, a dirty windshield can cause a blinding glare when lights hit it just the right way - just to be safe, always keep it clean, inside and out.
